{"tid":837283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿男人「腿張太開」…正妹怒噴漂白水　掀裙露內褲抗議","createTime":"2018-09-26T09:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T09:44:37.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fdbbe536cfa9d179b1ff814ba6e6aa101993b26a","tid":837283,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NCZOw05L7JA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNCZOw05L7JA&d=vqf9ZX9Fm6encRDPqvqyrJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7de78458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NCZOw05L7JA</a><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯一名20歲的法律系學生安娜（Anna Dovgalyuk），因認為俄羅斯男子普遍抱有「性別侵略性」，故想利用實際行動，來阻止這股風氣。安娜在地鐵上展開行動，她一上車就盯著那些「雙腳打開開」的男人看，隨後就拿出漂白水朝他們的下體噴，她表示「我要男人們留下不可抹滅的印記」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1559543-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1559543-XXL.jpg&h=23ac7c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1559540-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1559540-XXL.jpg&h=5432aec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，安娜自許為「社會運動人士」，她認為俄羅斯男人的沙文主義非常嚴重，故想要解決此問題。安娜以30公升水混6公升漂白水的比例，調配出超高濃度的洗潔劑，並朝那些在地鐵上將腿打開的男子下體潑灑，她指出「這個洗潔劑能夠在幾分鐘內造成布料退色，因此可以留下印記」，這樣能夠讓大家知道，這些男人都是用下半身來思考。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1559544-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1559544-XXL.jpg&h=573495bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這已經不是安娜第一次為女權發聲，她過去也曾在地鐵站掀起裙子、露出內褲，為表達出女性穿裙子常在地鐵遇到騷擾的問題。<span style=\"color: red;\">但卻有媒體認為安娜的影片都是假的，甚至指控她是請臨演來配合演出</span>，對此安娜回應「我的行動絕對是真的」！（編輯：林緯平）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=434256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D434256&d=vqf9ZX9Fm6encRDPqvqyrJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0cf45133\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D434256&h=2ce223b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=434256</a>"},{"pid":"dc2e46cf6571c41765a59a0370364dc5607d1c8e","tid":837283,"uid":56533,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"她過去也曾在地鐵站掀起裙子、露出內褲，為表達出女性穿裙子常在地鐵遇到騷擾的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/170412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F170412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=05b8d1b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7486a4e96d71b5fe3d47813541a713985e5330b","tid":837283,"uid":212268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：法律系<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe525747d39349f8766da81e2f34a594ff80848","tid":837283,"uid":6222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"女人著褲都可以擘脾坐嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fcf340307f0544b03020f4611e8846f3588670","tid":837283,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af18f5e0049e0c8a9bf5365f5e52a14fcf66dba","tid":837283,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc2e46cf6571c41765a59a0370364dc5607d1c8e","tid":837283,"uid":56533,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"她過去也曾在地鐵站掀起裙子、露出內褲，為表達出女性穿裙子常在地鐵遇到騷擾的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/170412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F170412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=05b8d1b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"真係諗唔明係咩邏輯嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211b3ab8447bb273ec154619ac689a7d715aeee3","tid":837283,"uid":109462,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1559544-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1559544-XXL.jpg&h=573495bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這已經不是安娜第一次為女權發聲，她過去也曾在地鐵站掀起裙子、露出內褲，為表達出女性穿裙子常在地鐵遇到騷擾的問題。</blockquote><br />\n呢種抗爭支持得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9075b182208f1ec53c1b134c208da97de0c88cea","tid":837283,"uid":101367,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"我係女人都唔撐佢 男人不嬲都腿張開咁坐架喇 佢無撚野呀"},{"pid":"07d8470f618e59197e8356e72c93d02403d2d780","tid":837283,"uid":199145,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"又係讀gender study讀到傻左既女權膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529e2857823ca58e35c5fc68a6913bf619b920c8","tid":837283,"uid":65887,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/11a/532/11a5329a31e7f6d636a25fb71883891a1b2279b0_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F11a%2F532%2F11a5329a31e7f6d636a25fb71883891a1b2279b0_b.jpg&h=dc0c154c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53a63bc1a497ad2be67cfc7289f4748da45797b7","tid":837283,"uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d7486a4e96d71b5fe3d47813541a713985e533